{"tid":1818881,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"幫台灣大選造下勢","createTime":"2020-01-10T09:47:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-11T05:38:08.000Z","uid":40443,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"99aeb5de7447fddaa4a8ddab84359350019c0691","tid":1818881,"uid":40443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T09:47:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ejub8C7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fejub8C7.png&h=b3939f8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔好意思做咗少少你標題黨<br />\n唔知有冇巴絲留意我地<br />\n但應該都有睇過我地啲work<br />\n今次喺葵芳連儂牆嗰度搞<br />\n依家仲好努力咁整緊<br />\n到時見到嘅話影張相打個卡啦哈哈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望台灣人見到我哋嘅心機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f22aa61a66b60c3c21760172733eee2801843e7","tid":1818881,"uid":40443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T09:47:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36d5157941ee85a596ee5f5e4d5064bc0d99066b","tid":1818881,"uid":40443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T09:48:09.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c1deac80367696a80e7063598cffd1820935ed5","tid":1818881,"uid":40443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T09:48:22.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"c09b95afa02d55df67a1128baf1e50560b3b85b9","tid":1818881,"uid":206141,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T09:48:30.000Z","msg":"樓豬好勁 正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/no